0:11:34.294,000 --> 0:11:37,000
Now, I'm not saying that Apple is the only company who has embraced

245
0:11:38.247,000 --> 0:11:4,000
the cult of simplicity.

246
0:11:40.827,000 --> 0:11:42,000
