265
0:12:32.193,000 --> 0:12:33,000
You do not.

266
0:12:33.408,000 --> 0:12:37,000
On the opposite side of the monitor, a task bar appears,

267
0:12:38.123,000 --> 0:12:41,000
and somewhere in those links -- by the way, not at the top --

268
0:12:41.909,000 --> 0:12:45,000
somewhere in those links is a button that makes you a new document.

269
0:12:46.377,000 --> 0:12:48,000
Ok, so that is a company not counting taps.

270
0:12:49.394,000 --> 0:12:52,000
You know, I don't want to just stand here and make fun of Microsoft ...

271
0:12:53.222,000 --> 0:12:54,000
Yes, I do.

272
0:12:54.548,000 --> 0:12:55,000
(Laughter)

273
0:12:56,000 --> 0:12:59,000
(Applause)

274
0:12:59.619,000 --> 0:13:,000
The Bill Gates song!

